NEET#,#NEET Advanced Materials Machines#,#Advanced Materials Machines#,#NEET Certificate in Advanced Materials Machines#,#url=https://neet.mit.edu/threads/amm
Learn to rapidly prototype and explore the novel materials, technologies and processes that will define the future of production. Discover how engineers scale up materials-intensive manufacturing enterprises from prototyping, production and then product and process innovation. Learn about additive manufacturing, 3D printing, powder and casting processes, advanced polymer processing approaches all applied to the aerospace, automotive, energy, and health care sectors!

proj_1
Recommended sophomore fall.
proj_2
Recommended junior year
capstone
Can be taken junior and/or senior year.
seminar
(Participation in 3 semesters over the course of 3 years, can do more)
foundation


